<section class="section aerys-proof" id="proof" aria-labelledby="proof-title">
  <div class="container">

    <span class="sec-label">Clinical Validation</span>
    <h2 id="proof-title" class="aerys-proof__headline">
      Medically endorsed.<br>Data-backed. <span class="hi">Third-party verified.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="aerys-proof__inner">

      <!-- Doctor column -->
      <div>
        <div class="aerys-medical__video">
          <img
            src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/bba426_9447cd68d99d45829e71e80fd75a1565~mv2.png"
            alt="Dr. Geoffrey Tomlin endorsing AERYS™"
            class="aerys-medical__video-thumb"
            width="560" height="350"
            loading="lazy"
          >
          <button class="aerys-medical__play" id="aerysMedVideoBtn" aria-label="Play Dr. Tomlin's clinical explanation">
            <div class="aerys-medical__play-btn">
              <svg class="aerys-medical__play-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
            </div>
          </button>
          <div class="aerys-medical__dr-badge">
            <div class="aerys-medical__dr-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="aerys-medical__dr-name">Dr. Verified</div>
              <div class="aerys-medical__dr-title">Medical Professional</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="aerys-medical__dr-credit" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="aerys-medical__dr-credit-name">Dr. Geoffrey Tomlin, DO, FACS</div>
            <div class="aerys-medical__dr-credit-spec">Otolaryngology &middot; H&amp;N Surgery</div>
            <div class="aerys-medical__dr-credit-spec">Facial Plastic Surgery</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="aerys-proof__quote">
          &ldquo;Mouth breathing during sleep is one of the most underestimated contributors to poor recovery, elevated cortisol, and long-term facial structural changes. A consistent nasal breathing habit &mdash; maintained through the night with a high-quality adhesive &mdash; can produce measurable differences in sleep architecture and morning recovery. The quality of the adhesive is not a minor detail. It determines whether the intervention actually works.&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
        <p class="aerys-proof__attribution"><strong>Dr. Geoffrey Tomlin, DO, FACS</strong><br>Otolaryngology &middot; Head &amp; Neck Surgery &middot; Facial Plastic Surgery</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats column -->
      <div>
        <div class="aerys-proof__stats">
          <div class="aerys-proof__stat">
            <div class="aerys-proof__stat-num">94%</div>
            <p class="aerys-proof__stat-label">of users reported measurable improvement in morning energy within their first 30-night protocol</p>
          </div>
          <div class="aerys-proof__stat">
            <div class="aerys-proof__stat-num">3.2&times;</div>
            <p class="aerys-proof__stat-label">increase in measured REM depth in users with documented mouth breathing habits, tracked across 90 nights</p>
          </div>
          <div class="aerys-proof__stat">
            <div class="aerys-proof__stat-num">68%</div>
            <p class="aerys-proof__stat-label">reduction in snoring frequency reported by partners of AERYS™ users after 30 nights of consistent use</p>
          </div>
          <div class="aerys-proof__stat">
            <div class="aerys-proof__stat-num">12 hrs</div>
            <p class="aerys-proof__stat-label">of secure, clean adhesion verified across all skin types, including sensitive skin and full facial hair</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="aerys-proof__badges" aria-label="Certifications">
          <span>HSA / FSA Eligible</span>
          <span>cGMP Certified</span>
          <span>Third-Party Tested</span>
          <span>FDA Registered</span>
        </div>

        <div class="aerys-proof__rating">
          <span class="stars" aria-label="4.9 out of 5 stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
          <span><strong>4.9 / 5</strong> &mdash; from 2,847 verified buyers</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Proof",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Proof" }]
}
{% endschema %}
